      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Al Husayn Bin Muhammad, from Moala Bin Muhammad, from Al Washa, from Aban, from Abdul Rahman Bin Abu Abdullah, ",
          "(It has been narrated) from Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup> regarding a man who insulted a man without slander, would he be treated harshly? Is there a Penalty (<span class=\"iTxt\">Hadd</span>) upon him?’ He<sup>asws</sup> said: ‘Upon him is the reprimanding’."
        ]
